review: Good enough no issue with the doctor. I visited for general fever treatment. The doctor's behaviour was good and listened to our problem. I wouldn't like to recommend this doctor to others because instead of treatment he used to do the right investigation. I would like to give a rating of 4/5. **** ** ***** ** *********** **** ***** ** ********* *********** ************* ** *** ******** ******* *** ******* ***** ** ******* *** ***** *** **** **************

Consulted to the doctor, he is a good doctor about treatment. Once I booked an appointment from Practo that time he is not available. Main thing is doctor timing because he will not be available sometimes. I would like to give a rating of 3.5/5 but he is good, honest. And I visited for my wife fever treatment and he prescribed medicine not reacted differently but he is good. There was waiting time while collecting medicine, It took a long time around half an hour.

Another person sitting next to doctor when I went in, doc was more concentrating to talk to him than me. *** ** *** **** *** ************** ****** **** **** ** * ***** Didn't listen to me, interrupted many times without empathy. Over all I felt wastage of my time n money.
Appointment was for 6.30 doctor came at around 7.30 had to wait for him to come and then after that for him to screen other patients...it took me around 3 hours for a normal check up
Doctor had prescribed exact medicines to cure the issue. Doctor's deep knowledge regarding my health issue understanding was good

review: Am not satisfied with doctor. Doctor is not explaining the problem. And not a talkative person. Thank you
